 See cost per play for your games.<br><br>BG Stats has export and import fu=
nctions for easy backup to a variety of services.<br>You can sync with othe=
r devices via BG Stats Cloud sync (an in-app subscription).<br>All in a nat=
ive interface, supporting dark mode on Android 10+, landscape and tablet sc=
reens.<br><br>With the Power Expansion (in-app purchase):<br>- Extended gam=
